flowRoot.flowPara: Pressing search enters the criteria into the search box.
Author and title searches are identified by an icon at the beginning of the tag.
Date chooser is displayed when the date field is focused.
If a file type is selected, relevant property fields are displayed.
Date chooser hides once a valid date has been entered. Date options are shown while a valid date is present - they hide when the date is cleared or edited.
Search options are displayed as tags in the search bar. They can be dismissed individually or as a whole.
Search options can be accessed from the search bar drop down.
Modifications to the search options are updated live and persist until 1) they are cleared from the search bar (see below) or 2) the search bar is retracted.
Date chooser is displayed when the date field is focused.
